  '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001',
  $escape$OWASP - Snyk: Automate Vulnerability Fixes in OWASP ZAP$escape$,
  $escape$When integrating Snyk with OWASP ZAP, use the 'zap-snyk' plugin to automate vulnerability fixes. Configure your ZAP API keys in the Snyk dashboard and set up container and IaC scans. Snyk will then scan your OWASP ZAP results for known vulnerabilities and provide fix PRs. Use the 'snyk test' command to run scans and integrate with your CI/CD pipeline.$escape$,
  $escape$snyk test --file=app.yaml --project=my-repo$escape$,
  $escape$bash$escape$,
